## Runtime.ResourceTree.IReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch interface

Interface for branch nodes in a resource tree that contain child nodes. Branch nodes organize the tree structure and cannot have resource values. If a path has child resources, it must be a branch and cannot itself be a resource.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface IReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch<T> extends IReadOnlyResourceTreeNode 
```
**Extends:** [IReadOnlyResourceTreeNode](./ts-res.runtime.resourcetree.ireadonlyresourcetreenode.md)
